---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Shop"
	description="Visit our in-clinic shop in Clapham for CBD gummies, recovery rollers, gift vouchers and a curated range of products to support your treatment and training."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Shop"
		highlight="Our"
		subtitle="A curated in-store shop at our Clapham clinic, stocked with the products our team trusts and recommends."
		breadcrumb="Shop"
		hideCta
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="In-store"
		heading="Recovery, performance and"
		highlight="rehab essentials"
		youtubeId="Ob8walH04XA"
		autoplay
		imageAlt="Video: Balance Physio shop tour"
	>
		<p>Support your recovery beyond the clinic. Our carefully selected range of rehabilitation products is designed to help you manage pain, improve mobility, and maintain progress at home. Speak to your physiotherapist for personalised recommendations.</p>
		<p>Our reception shop is open whenever the clinic is. We stock a considered range of products to help you protect, perform, recover and rehabilitate.</p>
		<p>Everything on the shelves has been chosen by our therapists for its quality and relevance to the work we do with our clients, so you can be confident you're picking up something we'd genuinely recommend.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Foam rollers, peanut balls and trigger point tools</li>
			<li>Resistance bands and rehab accessories</li>
			<li>Recovery and mobility products</li>
			<li>Athletic tape and supports</li>
		</ul>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Wellbeing"
		heading="CBD products and"
		highlight="gift vouchers"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/shop/cbd-capsules.jpg"
		imageAlt="CBD Brothers Blue Edition capsules on display in the Balance Physio shop"
	>
		<p>Explore our range of premium CBD products, selected to support relaxation and everyday wellbeing. Speak to our team to find the option that's right for you.</p>
		<p>Looking for a thoughtful gift? Our gift vouchers are redeemable across our services including physiotherapy, sports massage, strength &amp; conditioning and more. They make a meaningful gesture for someone you'd like to support on their health journey. Remember a gift voucher might be that perfect present for a post-race massage.</p>
		<p>Pop in to browse during clinic hours, or ask reception about gift vouchers when you next visit.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
